024300     MOVE    SPACE TO TEST-RESULTS.                               RW1014.2
024400     PERFORM  HEAD-ROUTINE THRU COLUMN-NAMES-ROUTINE.             RW1014.2
024500     GO TO CCVS1-EXIT.                                            RW1014.2
