041900     MOVE "FIRST GENERATE" TO FEATURE.                            RW1014.2
042000     PERFORM PRINT-DETAIL.                                        RW1014.2
042100 GENER-TEST-02.                                                   RW1014.2
042200     IF PAGE-COUNTER NOT EQUAL TO 1                               RW1014.2
