041600*                                                                 RW1044.2
041700*    OUTPUT REPORT INFORMATION                                    RW1044.2
041800*                                                                 RW1044.2
041900*        THE PAGE HEADING REPORT GROUP IS PRESENTED ON LINE 1     RW1044.2
042000*    OF PAGE 1.                                                   RW1044.2
