055000*    IS SET TO 6 WHEN THE DETAIL REPORT GROUP IS PRESENTED.       RW1044.2
055100*    REFERENCES  PAGE VIII-5, 2.4.5(4), LINE-COUNTER RULES        RW1044.2
055200*                PAGE VIII-19, 2.5.5.8.1(6)D, FINAL L-C SETTING   RW1044.2
